|pages=S209<U+2013>10
|year=2008
|month=September
|pmid=18690493
|doi=10.1007/s10072-008-0938-x
|url=
}}</ref> Several measures have been proposed but none is widely accepted.<ref name="pmid18690495">{{cite journal
|author=Furlan R
|title=Definition of non-responders: biological markers
|journal=Neurological sciences : official journal of the Italian Neurological Society and of the Italian Society of Clinical Neurophysiology
|volume=29 Suppl 2
