}}</ref> Nevertheless, the concept is widely used. For example, it is known that 30% of MS patients are non-responsive to Beta interferon.<ref name="pmid18690496">{{cite journal
|author=Bertolotto A, Gilli F
|title=Interferon-beta responders and non-responders. A biological approach
